gPodder 4 for Android
=====================

This repository contains the packaging scripts and metadata needed to build a
packaged version of gPodder 4 for Android >= 4.0 (API Level 14).


Requirements:

   - Android SDK
   - Android NDK (tested with r10c)
   - Qt 5.3.2 SDK for Android
   - PyOtherSide 1.4.0 for Android installed into QML plugins folder
     - Static build of Python 3 for Android
     - Embedded Python Standard Library

Included as Git submodules:

   - gPodder 4 Core
   - gPodder QML UI Reference Implementation
   - podcastparser
